    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.36.38a"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">38a</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">THE UNIVERSITY OF NEBRASKA 
                        <lb/>
                    LINCOLN, NEBRASKA 68508
                        <lb/>
                    
                    OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT</hi> 
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>April 10, 1972</dateline>
                    
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine> 
                        <addrLine>5835 Vine Street</addrLine> 
                        <addrLine>Lincoln, Nebraska</addrLine>
                    </address>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>It is my pleasure to tell you that the Board of Regents of the University of Nebraska has voted to confer upon you the Nebraska Builder Award.</p>
                
                <p>Presentation of the award will be a part of the Commencement exercises, Friday, May 19, in the Pershing Municipal Auditorium. It has always been customary for the recipients of this award to be present to receive it. We hope you can be with us that day. In the meantime, we shall appreciate your keeping the matter confidential until the University makes a public announcement.</p> 
                
                <p>Congratulations and best wishes!</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours truly,</salute>
                
                    <signed>D B Varner</signed> 
                    <signed>D. B. Varner
                    President</signed> 
                </closer>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">THE UNIVERISTY OF NEBRASKA-LINCOLN                      THE UNIVERSITY OF NEBRASKA AT OMAHA 
                        <lb/>
                                                            THE UNIVERSITY OF NEBRASKA MEDICAL CENTER</hi> 
                </fw>                
                
            </div1>
